Benjamin Salisbury https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benjamin_Salisbury 0 Benjamin David Salisbury (born October 19, 1980) is an American actor and dancer best known for playing the role of Brighton Sheffield on the CBS television sitcom The Nanny from 1993 to 1999.
